HEADWORD: Caperer
<hw>Ca"per*er</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>One who capers,
leaps, and skips about, or dances.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>The nimble <qex>caperer</qex> on the cord.</q>
<rj><qau>Dryden.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

